Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管回忆溢满心头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓在干掉的泪痕中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:01:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会以迎接朋友的方式\N温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#12爱情的危机!你明明说过爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4点20分,时间应该还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在干嘛\N居然西装笔挺的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员跟三鹰约…约会?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两张票很贵耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,是我啦,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空的话\N要不要一起去看个电影?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我有票,指定席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要请我看电影吗?\N真是难得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了,谁要请你啊\N你要给我付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?手头紧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有女朋友的话\N我就不会打电话给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思!\N你这种仿佛在取笑我的笑声!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没资格说我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且我可是好心邀你出来看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人要打电话,我挂了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是五代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在同一家酒店打工的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫七尾小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了,小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我没什么印象吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,因为我都在外头送货\N很少在店里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我对于人名\N一向不太记得住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你把眼镜拿下来\N简直变成另外一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把打工赚的钱\N拿去配了一副隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是打算买别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来突然买了隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜不出来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你大概也猜不出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊,这是电影票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,指定席
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这部电影很受女生欢迎耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么听说\N才特地去买的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔,我好想看这部电影喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意的话\N要不要一起去看?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N好像是我硬要你带我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说,我也正愁没人陪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会造成你的困扰吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员和三鹰到哪里去了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,现在他们两个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?快点走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们改走另外一条路\N走另外一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?车站就在前面耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正走就对了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你是五代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也出来约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不能小看你\N居然把手放在人家肩上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我以前打工的同事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧,电影要来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个真是速配的一对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明跟我说他爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却有个那么年轻可爱的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过份了\N竟然玩弄女人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,不快点的话\N我们的音乐会也要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,再一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不原谅你!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在说你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这种电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好没有找管理员来看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她是管理员就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(莫札特)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场音乐会好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能约你一起来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次请再跟我一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,如果你愿意邀我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的\N能和你这样在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况,今晚你真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,只有今晚而已吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好坏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然有个那么\N年轻可爱的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,我们找个地方吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还想辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不像男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以喝一点酒吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开车,所以不能喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N我不会叫你喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心\N看来暂时会吃不下饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然黏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们平常都是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横滨有个夜景很美的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你方便的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,横滨可能太远了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是横滨还是哪里\N我都陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究…究竟是怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能问你一件事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天愿意和我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了想去听音乐会而已吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其它的理由是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能够让我远离管理员工作\N松口气的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一个男人而言呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也有女朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也?你有男朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,我不是在说我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有什么男朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以问你一件事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的电影\N你原本是想跟谁去看?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路上遇见的那个女人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是\N她有个很登对的男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管原本要跟谁去看\N我今天真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起很无聊吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊,你很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴喔\N换了隐形眼镜终于有了价值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过这座公园可以抄近路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常我都走商店街回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有你陪着我\N所以我不用害怕,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定反而会更恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑,我是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然问这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你愿意把我当女人看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.11,0:15:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是打工的同事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被一时的感情冲昏了头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是吻一下应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我…我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小津江…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次还能见面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩是不是对我有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吓人好不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么眼神?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有做任何不轨的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有一瞬间曾经犹豫过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过结果我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么叫得这么悲伤呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么,不是管理员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员还没回来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,都已经11点半了说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,不可以逃避现实喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候喝酒最好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么跟什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要随便跑进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来分担你的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有什么不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说到三鹰这个男人\N手脚好像很快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,那个眼神很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员她不会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,管理员对这种事\N没有什么免疫力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个涉世未深的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很容易被浪漫的气氛迷住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:20:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜雾包围着我们幽会的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想说\N夜雾,今晚也谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要难过\N痛快喝个两杯把一切都忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,已经这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她今晚大概会外宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔一两次早上回来也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,又不是小孩子的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,喝吧\N反正今晚她也不会回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,结果弄到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,不过我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以再约你出来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不要只为了松口气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌到谷底,坠入痛苦的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求幸福\N却坠入痛苦的深渊里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了,被甩了,被讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好借酒浇愁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来喝一杯好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走,睡觉去,睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我!放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:22:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去,冷静一点,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我!放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候不能去打扰人家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的力量真伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认输了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以,求求你,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,不可以这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的西装弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛,真令人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得应该说无聊呢?\N还是有趣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,三更半夜的不要发出\N那种会引人误会的叫声啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:23:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在期待些什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续喝,继续喝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.56,0:23:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也进来喝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有很多女人打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.77,0:23:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且每天打,打个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N‘万人迷的五代?当心桃色电话!’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代竟然笑眯眯的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么嘛,那个色小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.26,0:24:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光只是眨个眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.71,0:24:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.72,0:24:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.09,0:24:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经可以相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.50,0:25:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.87,0:25:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快要忍受不了\N快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.45,0:25:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是痛苦的折磨

